        code: '# Set output style to Explanatory\n/config\n# → Output style → Explanatory\n# Now Claude explains WHY, not just WHAT\n\n# Ask for visual explanations:\n"Generate a visual HTML presentation explaining this codebase."\n"Draw an ASCII diagram of the authentication flow."\n\n# Other output styles:\n# Explanatory — learn new codebases\n# Learning — Claude coaches you through changes\n# Custom — create your own voice',
